    AmplNLWriter.relation_to_nl
    AmplNLWriter.replace_variableindex_by_int — Function.

    MathProgBase expects expressions with variables denoted by x[i] for contiguous i. However, JuMP 0.19 creates expressions with x[MOI.VariableIndex(i)]. So we have to recursively walk the expression replacing instances of MOI.VariableIndex by a corresponding integer.
